# E-Commerce Sales Performance Platform

## Project Overview
This project is a comprehensive sales analysis solution created to track 340M in revenue across global markets. By transforming over 14,000 rows of raw data into an interactive visual interface, this dashboard allows users to filter by Month, Country, Year, and Category to find instant business insights.

## Final Dashboard Preview
![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/231055a7-298d-4d8a-84ae-20cc6dd9050d)


## Key Features & Metrics
* **Core KPIs**: Real-time tracking of Net Sales ($340M), Total Orders (5000), and Average Order Value (â‚¹68,004).
* **Automated Insights**: Dynamic "Best Category" indicator that updates based on slicer selection (e.g., Fashion).
* **Regional Intelligence**: Interactive Map Chart visualizing sales volume across key regions including India, USA, UK, Australia and Germany.
* **Product Performance**: Top 5 Products bar chart and Sales by Category analysis.

## Technical Implementation
* **Data Modeling**: Integrated Fact and Dimension tables using Power Pivot for a clean star schema.
* **DAX Formulas**: Developed custom measures for Total Net Sales and dynamic text-based rankings.
* **Advanced UI**: Utilized synchronized slicers, customized map projections, and a "Don't move or size with cells" layout to ensure a stable user experience.

## How to Use
1. Download the file.
2. Open in Excel and ensure "Enable Content" is selected for Power Pivot.
3. Use the slicer panel on the bottom left to filter the entire dashboard.
